                 beyond the nucleation limit, which allows us to improve
                 the precision of the trained ANNs and make the theory
                 predictions more accurate. Also we develop an
                 approximate approach, which requires smaller and
                 simpler MD data for training, but gives the strain rate
                 dependence of the nucleation threshold close to the
                 rigorous theory of dislocation nucleation.},
