                 rates corresponding to a scenario where low density of
                 defects alternates at irregular times with high
                 populations of defects. We propose a simple stochastic
                 model of dislocation reaction kinetics that is able to
                 capture these statistical properties of the dislocation
                 density fluctuations as a function of shear rate.},
