                 epitaxy, together with several other new methods that
                 have been successfully developed in the past few years.
                 On the basis of the extraordinary electrical and
                 functional properties and thermal--mechanical
                 stability, the applications of hBN-based nanosheets as
                 substrates and dielectrics, passivation layers, and
                 nanofillers in nanodevices and nanocomposites are
                 discussed, together with the peculiar optical and
                 wetting characteristics.},
